
    What problem do they solve by only permitting code rollouts twice a day?
    To prevent more instabilities by introducing code that was affecting performance to their systems
    
    Why are they afraid of the auditors?
    Because they have all of these pieces of paper from faxes with the CVV numbers writen on them after they swipped the credit cards
    
    What is a NOC?  (It’s mentioned in the book and we’ve talked about it in class, but you may have to google it)
    Network Operations Center, a monitor center that has a broad knowledge of the health of the network in companies, they are the first to notice any kind of issues going on with the network.
    
    Why do Bill and Chris decide to meet once a week?
    To try figure out how to avoid for IT to get outsourced after what Steve said at their meeting.
